name: Resilient
description: I have faced many challenges in my life, as many of us have faced. I never gave it much thought, I am surprised that I've lived this long. Then my friend @FendelMarc used the word Resilient, to described me one day. With the support of Marc, and Jayne, I felt like I have achieved a lot in this NFT Community. I'm excited about my life, and the future.
